<h2 id="need-help-found-a-bug">Need Help? Found a bug?</h2>

<p><a href="https://github.com/lord/slate/issues">Submit an issue</a> to the Slate Github if you need any help. And, of course, feel free to submit pull requests with bug fixes or changes.</p>

